{"tid":1037972,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"終於輪到我","createTime":"2019-02-26T10:22:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T10:43:41.000Z","uid":68999,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"97db35aea3c5ed042b85ced5b615bc4af744a390","tid":1037972,"uid":68999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T10:22:59.000Z","msg":"5年幾感情<br />\n一早已經視佢做結婚對象<br />\n一直以佢做目標 努力儲錢想結婚<br />\n一句話淡左就淡左<br />\n做幾多野都無用<br />\n好似去到邊都有同佢既回憶咁<br />\n<br />\n男人真係唔可以窮<br />\n宜家份糧想儲錢結婚就得翻好少錢用<br />\n條女只會怪你無事業<br />\n唔會同你一齊捱<br />\n唔會一齊努力"},{"pid":"7fccc7fee9376fc3a30ecd3bfda475777ce5ef7b","tid":1037972,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T10:24:44.000Z","msg":"好人好者捱乜春"},{"pid":"7f39d5f53806714785a3ec7012fcbf10b00834d3","tid":1037972,"uid":68999,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7fccc7fee9376fc3a30ecd3bfda475777ce5ef7b","tid":1037972,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T10:24:44.000Z","msg":"好人好者捱乜春"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T10:25:56.000Z","msg":"啱呀 大把人揀"},{"pid":"36d6371367ce7cd08114e9953cc116ffaff5544a","tid":1037972,"uid":190818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T10:32:15.000Z","msg":"早知，早走，早著<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"217bbdf8b464a9d36e664b847da2d8ea6a578926","tid":1037972,"uid":53194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T10:32:20.000Z","msg":"你不是還有錢嗎"},{"pid":"952dc2241b2fb5596fb0580a11768c0e20dad93a","tid":1037972,"uid":54787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T10:33:57.000Z","msg":"換轉諗，第時結左婚比人分半層樓仲慘啦<br />\n<br />\n比心機賺多個錢搵個更好啦"},{"pid":"f4651eeff138d31d40ac16e0a8542c8f9dac9cd5","tid":1037972,"uid":68999,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T10:36:00.000Z","msg":"曾經我真係好天真以為佢同普通港女唔同<br />\n肯一齊捱下 唔介意人地點睇<br />\n現實係天下烏鴉一樣黑"},{"pid":"0c9aaf466dbdec57656b984321068b686975406c","tid":